Enum ResourceType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ResourceType>
      • constants.ResourceType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnumValue, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ResourceType>

    public enum ResourceType
extends java.lang.Enum<ResourceType>
implements EnumValue
    Resource codes used in an Object entry. They defines the resource the resource contains/the building can receive.
    Author:
    MarcoForlini
